ontent/uploads/2025/03/kelly_clarkson_show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kelly_clarkson_show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kelly_clarkson_show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯利·克拉克森（Kelly Clarkson）</a>庆祝了她的美国聊天节目的第1000集，分享了她自演出开始以来“失去了很多”。</p><p> “自从您离开以来”歌手于2019年9月开始主持<i>凯利·克拉克森（Kelly Clarkson）的演出</i>，此后在NBC的工作日下午播出。在星期四（3月20日），她主持了地标情节，并与现场观众分享了一个情感开放的独白。</p><p>她说：“我简直不敢相信今天是第1000名，这太疯狂了。” “我们遇到了一些很有才华的人，大量的大明星和鼓舞人心的日常英雄。”</p><p>她继续谈到该节目在五年半播出的挑战，包括导航的Covid-19。她补充说：“个人也很多起伏。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯利·克拉克森（Kelly Clarkson）庆祝第1000集！" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cyFFZ2khkVg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “在1,000集中，我们一起笑了起来，我们一起哭了，与美丽的故事一起哭泣，一起唱歌，一起跳舞，庆祝并一起竞争”。</p><p>她继续说：“我一个人失去了很多。” “And along the way, we found comfort in one another. And looking back, we are all incredibly proud of what we&#39;ve built and the community we&#39;ve created. I am grateful to everyone who has been part of this journey. It has been such a cool time. Thank you so much.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-speaks-about-extraordinarily-hard-post-divorce-depression-3566394">Clarkson spoke openly last year about the “extraordinarily hard” depression that she went through</a> following her divorce from Brandon Blackstock in 2022. The couple share two children, and reflecting on the separation, she said: “You feel alone, and it&#39;s just a blessing to be able to have that outlet [of making music and hosting her show] for those emotions that are overwhelming.”</p><p> The singer has faced <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-kelly-clarkson-show-is-toxic-behind-the-scenes-employees-claim-3442808">allegations that the show has been a toxic work environment</a> in the past, with members of staff accusing producers of “overworking” and “underpaying” employees. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-addresses-allegations-of-toxic-work-environment-on-her-talk-show-3443616">Clarkson said the team would reinforce a positive work environment</a> by introducing new leadership training for all current employees.</p><p> <i>The Kelly Clarkson Show</i> is well known for its &#39;Kellyoke&#39; segment, in which the host performs esoteric cover versions of beloved pop and alternative classics, including in recent times <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-billie-eilishs-birds-of-a-feather-3833076">Billie Eilish&#39;s &#39;Birds Of A Feather&#39;</a> , as well as tracks by <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-perform-say-it-aint-so-with-weezer-3757532">Weezer</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-and-miranda-lambert-cover-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-3796838">Chappell Roan</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-kelly-clarkson-covering-the-last-dinner-partys-nothing-matters-3776455">The Last Dinner Party</a> , and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-my-chemical-romances-welcome-to-the-black-parade-3093805">My Chemical Romance</a> , among others.它还诞生了克拉克森（Clarkson）在2022年的EP。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-says-she-has-lost-a-lot-as-she-marks-1000th-episode-of-chat-show-3848280">Kelly Clarkson says she has “lost a lot” as she marks 1,000th episode of chat show</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
